http://www.anythingbutipod.com/archives/2006/11/microsoft-zune-av-cable-pinouts.php&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot; target=&quot;_NEW&quot;&gt;
http://www.anythingbutipod.com/archives/2006/11/microsoft-zune-av-cable-pinouts.php&lt;/a&gt;

12) Stream to your PS3 or Xbox 360 using TVersity, refer to: &lt;a href=&quot;
http://tversity.com/&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot; target=&quot;_NEW&quot;&gt;
http://tversity.com/&lt;/a&gt;

